# 🔒 Securelic Vulnerability Scanners List

A comprehensive list of security scanners and tools provided by [Securelic](https://securelic.com) for securing networks, servers, web applications, and APIs.

## 📝 Overview

Securelic is an open-source powered vulnerability scanner designed to help organizations:

* Discover their attack surface 🌐  
* Scan for CVEs 🛡️  
* Manage security risks through automated workflows ⚙️  

## 🛠️ Scanners & Features

| Scanner Name | Description | Key Features |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **🌐 Attack Surface Discovery** | Continuously maps external footprints. | Subdomain identification, live service detection, open port mapping, technology fingerprinting. |
| **💻 Network & Infrastructure Scanner** | Scans servers and network assets for weaknesses. | Multi-layer scanning, misconfiguration detection, outdated components identification. |
| **🌟 Web Application Scanner (DAST)** | Automated penetration testing for modern web apps. | Injection flaws, broken authentication, insecure redirects, XSS detection. |
| **🔗 API Security Scanner** | Specialized testing for REST and GraphQL APIs. | Endpoint analysis, input validation, logical vulnerability detection. |
| **⚠️ CVE & Vulnerability Engine** | Deep engine for identifying known exposures. | Critical CVEs, runtime flaws, zero-day detection using updated databases. |
| **🔒 SSL/TLS & Certificate Analyzer** | Evaluates cryptographic health. | Certificate expiration tracking, TLS version checks, cipher strength analysis. |
| **✅ Compliance Validator** | Maps findings to global security standards. | GDPR, HIPAA, PCI DSS, ISO 27001 alignment. |
| **🔄 Continuous Pentesting** | Automated and ongoing security validation. | DevSecOps integration, real-time threat monitoring, automated regression testing. |

## ⚙️ Technical Capabilities

* **🔍 Advanced Fingerprinting:** Identifies tech stacks and service versions automatically.  
* **📊 Actionable Reporting:** Generates detailed reports with risk prioritization and remediation guidance.  
* **⏱️ Real-time Monitoring:** Continuously tracks infrastructure changes and security header regressions.  
* **🧩 Open Source Core:** Powered by industry-standard open-source security engines.  

## 🚀 Integration & Deployment

Securelic fits into modern development pipelines:

* **☁️ SaaS / Cloud-native:** No complex on-premise setup required.  
* **🔧 DevSecOps Ready:** Automated triggers for continuous security.  

